[{"client_msg_id":"09aa6cb0-9bac-4036-8ab1-5183c5b2dca5","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"継承も委譲も、うまくいく条件はあるし、あえば合理的かつ便利なんですよね。","ts":"1614477409.118100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"GcUfj"}]},{"client_msg_id":"2cee9464-5b7a-45a1-b3ec-b861229bee95","type":"message","user":"UERCTTT8B","text":"自分は大規模ゲーム書いた経験がないのでなんともわからんなあ","ts":"1614456185.115900","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"Cgq0"}]},{"client_msg_id":"5ca9fdf7-bea6-43d1-93b6-acb69475e7aa","type":"message","user":"UERCTTT8B","text":"\u0026gt; I'm going to have to give a hard disagree. I've been making my own engines for a long time, and have used many different engines for a longer time. Inheritance-based entity systems are often a pain in the ass to work with, a massive pain in the ass to debug, and tend to invite shitty hacks to get around the shortcomings of the inheritance model.","ts":"1614456111.115500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"98O"}]},{"client_msg_id":"694ff52c-d68a-4511-9587-94fd2ce51694","type":"message","user":"UERCTTT8B","text":"\u003chttps://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=26284158\u003e もめもめしている","ts":"1614456076.115000","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"eyes","count":1,"users":["UKHUVMBJR"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"k=QI"}]},{"client_msg_id":"e9fa7d3e-afb8-4b9c-b3bc-59758c1419ed","type":"message","user":"UKHUVMBJR","text":"コンポジションで済むならそうしたいですしねえ","ts":"1614451614.114800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"olbVm"}]},{"client_msg_id":"30569cec-777f-4fdd-9f2b-9b8e7e585bda","type":"message","user":"UERCTTT8B","text":"ただ継承が正義な場所ってそんな多くないと思うんですよね…","ts":"1614451485.114000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":fal